[install minikube]

https://kubernetes.io/fr/docs/setup/learning-environment/minikube/

1) install virtual box (msc)
2) brew install kubernetes-cli
3) chmod +x ./kubectl
4) brew install minikube
5) minikube start --vm-driver=virtualbox       # rm -rf ~/.minikube  ==> nettoyer

[Dashboard]

minikube addons enable dashboard # 
minikube dashboard

